{"tid":875992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★HSBC俾人狙擊？】滙豐最強空軍曝光！　\"橋水\"沽空1億股","createTime":"2018-10-25T09:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T12:51:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b52603fd34cd75dbe0b9c24ff1b309b2bb94dc67","tid":875992,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:22:48.000Z","msg":"股王滙豐控股﹙0005﹚下周一﹙29日﹚公布季績，惟股價近日明顯乏力，遠跑輸大市。有報道更指全球最大對冲基金橋水（Bridgewater）早於今年3月已沽空滙控，涉逾1億股，堪稱滙控最大「空軍」！<br />\n<br />\n截至中午收市，滙控報60.65元，挫1.5%，雖然守住60關，惟股價創下52周新低。該股下周一公布季績，自然成為市場焦點，但原來已有基金「提前」出手沽出滙控！<br />\n<br />\n有本地傳媒引述彭博數據顯示，全球最大對冲基金橋水（Bridgewater）於3月23日時申報在倫敦交易所累計沽空逾1億股滙控，相當於流通市值約0.5%。按當日收市價約為74港元計，橋水7個月內帳面獲利19%或13億港元（未計利息成本）。報道又指，截至目前為止，<span style=\"color: red;\">暫未見橋水的平倉紀錄。<br />\n</span><br />\n<strong>沽空率連續6日超過50%</strong><br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，滙控本港昨日沽空率﹙沽空佔成交金額﹚達50.3%，一連6日超過50%。而按證監最新數據，截至10月12日，滙控已申報淡倉達1.114億股，金額達73.6億元，而對上一星期﹙10月5日﹚，該股申報淡倉則為7,691.7萬股，淡倉金額52.64億元。換言之，滙控淡倉股數及金額一周內分別急升44.8%及39.8%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/251072/%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E6%A9%8B%E6%B0%B4%E6%B2%BD%E7%A9%BA1%E5%84%84%E8%82%A1-%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E6%B7%A1%E5%80%89%E6%95%B8%E6%8C%89%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%A6%E9%A3%8645\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F251072%2F%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B1%2590%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589-%25E6%25A9%258B%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25B2%25BD%25E7%25A9%25BA1%25E5%2584%2584%25E8%2582%25A1-%25E7%2594%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%25B7%25A1%25E5%2580%2589%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%258C%2589%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%25A6%25E9%25A3%258645&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkgtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=8ecf494c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/251072/%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E7%A9%BA%E8%BB%8D%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89-%E6%A9%8B%E6%B0%B4%E6%B2%BD%E7%A9%BA1%E5%84%84%E8%82%A1-%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E6%B7%A1%E5%80%89%E6%95%B8%E6%8C%89%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%A6%E9%A3%8645</a>"},{"pid":"7d37c33ffb8c918e33c9b3d2fee8ada68c72a50e","tid":875992,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa3b3b58610d76e259517d4de8a448abe53602c","tid":875992,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:23:39.000Z","msg":"會否執？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9fc1cfc614df5bac3f6e179c4b9b64509564a9","tid":875992,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bb735b834f1d93350f705140a894e201a64673","tid":875992,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfa3b3b58610d76e259517d4de8a448abe53602c","tid":875992,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:23:39.000Z","msg":"會否執？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"不如腦魔收購咗佢"},{"pid":"4d4abc1dd4da766924c44282c7e60b0d241e4a97","tid":875992,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:50:26.000Z","msg":"得到腦魔詛咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im